^B__/^YRecent Changes^B\_____________________________________________________________^n
 - Better support for Crystal and standard telnet clients
 - New command 'promote' to increase your staff level
 - 'examine' now works on both users and socials
 - New command 'games' lists all current games in progress
 - Removed 'save' command, just set a password to save for the first time
 - Staff names are shown in a different colour during communication
 - Othello is down for maintenance
 - Quiz is down for maintenance
 - Connect 4 is down for maintenance
 - Steal is down for maintenance
 - Groups system has been removed
